                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Looks like a good system to me.
<br />

<br />
Even a hasted mob hitting for 500 - 700 is a good 450ish dps, well beyond that which most non-ubers can sustain for any amount of time.
<br />
 
<br />
